      "text": "Submit:  pg_dump → S3,  capture final commit SHA in attempt repo,  sb.kill(),  status='killed' → grading pipeline.\nReconciler (every 60s):  any sandbox without a session row is killed; any session past idle window is paused/expired. Truth converges in ≤ 60s.",
